      <title>选举意外出炉 全球基金对印度股市持谨慎态度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/global-funds-cautious-on-indian-stocks-after-election-surprise</link>
      <description><![CDATA[外国投资者在印度股票的空头仓位接近历史高位，凸显出即使在总理纳伦德拉·莫迪赢得盟友的关键支持以组建政府之后，投资者仍保持谨慎态度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/global-funds-cautious-on-indian-stocks-after-election-surprise</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 07:26:41 GMT</pubDate>
