      <title>欧洲央行官员警告不要急于进一步降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/ecb-s-kazaks-says-any-further-rate-cuts-need-to-be-gradual</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行官员对进一步降息的前景做出了谨慎的评估，寻求更多通胀进展的证据，以确保任何宽松政策都是合理的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/ecb-s-kazaks-says-any-further-rate-cuts-need-to-be-gradual</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 05:44:54 GMT</pubDate>
